<main>
    <%- include('../partials/studentSidebar') %>

    <div id="main-wrapper" style="background: #f4f4f4; min-height: 100vh; padding: 40px;">

        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="bg-white p-4 shadow-sm rounded mb-4" style="border: 1px solid #ddd; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
            <h5 class="m-0 fw-bold" style="color: #333;">📚 Rules and Regulations</h5>
        </div>

        <!-- Rules Section -->
        <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded shadow-sm" 
             style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 2; color: #444; border: 1px solid #ddd; max-width: 90%; margin: 0 auto;">

            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
                <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <span style="color: #28a745; font-size: 24px; margin-right: 12px;">✔️</span>
                    Everyone is required to maintain silence in the library.
                </li>

                <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <span style="color: #007bff; font-size: 24px; margin-right: 12px;">🔍</span>
                    Students can directly search for books and their availability using the website.
                </li>

                <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <span style="color: #ff5722; font-size: 24px; margin-right: 12px;">📚</span>
                    A book will be issued against a student only after showing their authorized library card.
                </li>

                <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <span style="color: #17a2b8; font-size: 24px; margin-right: 12px;">💻</span>
                    Students are requested to check their loans on the website regularly.
                </li>

                <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <span style="color: #ffc107; font-size: 24px; margin-right: 12px;">⏳</span>
                    A student can keep a book for a maximum of <strong>7 days</strong>, after which it must be returned.
                </li>

                <li style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <span style="color: #dc3545; font-size: 24px; margin-right: 12px;">⚠️</span>
                    Violation of rules and any act of misbehavior towards library staff will lead to strict disciplinary action.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </div>
</main>
